data.description:
Awesome, super sharp, totally updated brick colonial. This move in ready colonial features 3 nice sized bedrooms, 2,5 bathrooms and 2 car garage. As you enter you are welcomed by a large living room with fireplace that opens to the beautiful updated kitchen and formal dining room. The kitchen is updated with granite counter tops, back splash, stainless steel appliances, new cabinets and an oversized island! Very cozy sun room overlooking private backyard. The second floor features sizable bedrooms and recently updated bathrooms. Oversized master bedroom has a walk-in closet and recently updated oversized full bathroom. Finished basement with an updated half bath has a nature stone flooring.
Close in proximity to Lake Erie, Briardale Greens Golf Course, several parks, and freeway access. The seller is including one year home warranty with America's Preferred. Make this your new home!
